          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老汉钟元圃。吾儿钟子期。在集贤村居住。只因去年我儿在马鞍山前砍柴，遇"
        },
        {
          "character": "钟元圃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一晋国大夫俞伯牙与我儿共谈琴律，十分相得，结为金兰之好。临别之时，又"
        },
        {
          "character": "钟元圃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "赠吾儿黄金二笏，作为甘旨之资。不想吾儿回至家中，昼夜攻读，朝思暮想，"
        },
        {
          "character": "钟元圃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "他、他、他竟自一命而亡了。今乃百日之期，拿些纸钱与他焚化。唉！儿呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "钟元圃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "天哪！"
        },
        {
          "character": "钟元圃",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "家藏美玉终何用，膝下无儿一场空！"
        },
        {
          "character": "钟元圃",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老年丧子泪难忍，"
        },
        {
          "character": "钟元圃",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "抛下了我二老受孤贫！"
        },
        {
          "character": "钟元圃",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "白发人反送了黑发人。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（钟元圃下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [],
      "stats": {
        "line_counts": {
          "stage_direction": 5,
          "唱": 1
        },
        "singing_ratio": 1.0,
        "dominant_style_family": null,
        "musical_styles": []
      },
      "scene_feature": [
        1.0,
        0.4545,
        0.4545,
        0.0909,
        0.0,
